Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.38,0:00:02.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 梅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.98,0:00:05.98,Warning,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\be3\blur3}翻译：梅子 熊猫 校对：小白 时间：猫 后期：Waltz 压制：Waltz
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.57,0:00:03.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凪就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.23,0:00:14.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好甜 好咸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.85,0:00:21.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好甜 好辣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.04,0:00:33.53,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday　言葉がたりなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.04,0:00:33.53,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨日 言语不足以表达
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.92,0:00:43.71,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,すれ違ったとしても やめないで
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.92,0:00:43.71,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使词不达意 也不放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.57,0:00:50.88,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もっとわかりたい
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.57,0:00:50.88,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想更了解你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.85,0:01:04.08,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時にひとりになりたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.85,0:01:04.08,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时 想一人独处
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.89,0:01:15.27,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅をしても心は埋まらない そして
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.89,0:01:15.27,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使旅行 内心的空虚也无法填补
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.34,0:01:20.16,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大切な人に気づくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.34,0:01:20.16,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到我意识到你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.24,0:01:24.34,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いつもいつも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.24,0:01:24.34,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每时每刻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.45,0:01:31.36,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そう　うまくいくとは限らない毎日
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.45,0:01:31.36,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些有点小挫折的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.97,0:01:34.41,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,だけど笑って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.97,0:01:34.41,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你微笑面对
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.91,0:01:37.89,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君がくれた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.91,0:01:37.89,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的话语
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.17,0:01:45.46,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,たったひとことがどれほど嬉しかったか
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.17,0:01:45.46,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是多么令我开心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.00,0:01:50.83,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ずっとずっと覚えてる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.00,0:01:50.83,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直至今日我也无法忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.96,0:01:58.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.71,0:02:01.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我买了惠喜欢的高菜饭团哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.47,0:02:10.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笹野
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.98,0:02:11.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑泽君
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.13,0:02:13.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北川呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.60,0:02:16.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出版社说联系不到北川了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.92,0:02:19.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敲门也不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.04,0:02:21.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…怎么做才好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.54,0:02:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北川
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.53,0:02:34.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在吗 北川
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.69,0:02:36.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大和君
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.14,0:02:37.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.97,0:02:39.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.48,0:02:40.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以说给我听…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.68,0:02:41.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.87,0:02:42.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠 开门
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.93,0:02:43.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不开
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.98,0:02:45.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁让你来的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.72,0:02:47.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.58,0:02:48.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.86,0:02:50.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是多余的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.72,0:02:51.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁也不需要我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.10,0:02:52.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.87,0:02:54.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也这么想的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.26,0:02:57.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎样都与你无关
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.41,0:02:59.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别跟我装朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.59,0:03:01.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.04,0:03:04.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我受够了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.73,0:03:06.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受够了被人利用被人嘲笑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.27,0:03:09.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想跟我好的时候装朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.20,0:03:11.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正都会背叛我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.98,0:03:13.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就不需要朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.00,0:03:15.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.41,0:03:20.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.83,0:03:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我一个人呆着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.70,0:03:25.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北川
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.51,0:03:31.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就如刚才北川所说 有人就喜欢一个人呆着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.12,0:03:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人总是会背叛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.20,0:03:36.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不需要朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.10,0:03:38.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.35,0:03:39.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友只会让你受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.24,0:03:41.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不是所有人都这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.24,0:03:45.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有人会想帮你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.03,0:03:47.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人想着你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.22,0:03:49.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好好看看周围吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.23,0:03:53.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么关着自己不会有任何改变的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.66,0:03:55.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也什么都做不了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.84,0:03:59.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这样是在伤害担心你的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.94,0:04:03.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.41,0:04:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是我太软弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.01,0:04:09.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你孤单了 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.68,0:04:11.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你要道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.31,0:04:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠现在为什么伤心我都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.55,0:04:19.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你说给我听我可能也不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.19,0:04:22.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我想听你说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.67,0:04:24.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你妈妈也很担心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.61,0:04:25.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.59,0:04:27.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱怨也好 向我发火也好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.08,0:04:32.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为了让大家高兴做了这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.03,0:04:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都没用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.96,0:04:38.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再努力 也不被重视
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.93,0:04:40.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人需要我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.03,0:04:43.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家没有一个人需要我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.76,0:04:45.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.92,0:04:51.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别人怎么想有什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.03,0:04:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠从小时候开始就很努力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.58,0:04:56.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变得很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.21,0:04:58.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在也被很多人认识
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.48,0:05:01.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些都是真实的 这样不就够了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.74,0:05:04.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要自己毁掉这些努力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.54,0:05:10.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直觉得惠是所有人里最棒的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.20,0:05:13.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 惠就是惠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.36,0:05:16.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己觉得自己最棒就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.81,0:05:20.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我一直在你身边支持你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.88,0:05:24.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠个子好高真好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.31,0:05:26.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为最丑才站在最后边的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.33,0:05:28.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用管他们说什么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.87,0:05:33.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 果然很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.04,0:05:40.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要再自信一点啦 惠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.09,0:05:51.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论什么时候都在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.11,0:05:54.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直听着我说的话的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.53,0:06:11.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小桃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.75,0:06:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.16,0:06:17.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.17,0:06:38.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠回去工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.17,0:06:42.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.39,0:06:54.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.51,0:06:57.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.65,0:07:00.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心里放下一块大石头呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.26,0:07:03.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的? 这个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.11,0:07:08.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(惠 收   妈妈)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.32,0:07:15.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…能接受这样的自己吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.22,0:07:19.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能有所改变吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.87,0:07:31.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脆弱的心会伤害别人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.06,0:07:41.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(区区一个低水准读模 别拽了)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.28,0:07:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我要为至今做的蠢事付出的代价
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.42,0:07:57.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要做这种事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.15,0:07:59.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.10,0:08:01.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙根本就不在乎桃子你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.81,0:08:03.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是为了桃子才…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.26,0:08:05.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们没被她怎么样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.48,0:08:07.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们只是嫉妒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.76,0:08:09.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么呢你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.03,0:08:10.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了 别管她了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.90,0:08:13.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑 傻子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.63,0:08:22.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人为什么会越陷越深
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.38,0:08:25.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.32,0:08:28.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.12,0:08:31.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你拿着我的桌子干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.78,0:08:33.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.37,0:08:34.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在帮你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.33,0:08:35.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真过分
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.35,0:08:38.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.70,0:08:42.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想把它搬进教室去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.86,0:08:44.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你要帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.08,0:08:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我实在看不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.35,0:08:49.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠是个很温柔的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.52,0:08:51.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我看不下去这种事了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.99,0:08:53.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.00,0:08:56.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前的那个惠并不是真正的我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.81,0:09:00.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时我只是为了好办事 才对你好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.07,0:09:05.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 但我只记得惠对我好温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.81,0:09:08.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时常会带我出去玩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.10,0:09:12.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算惠你说这不是你所谓的温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.78,0:09:14.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我还是很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.64,0:09:17.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并不讨厌惠你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.84,0:09:24.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇到这样的事也没什么的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.14,0:09:26.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有比这更过分的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.62,0:09:27.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早已习惯这些了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.59,0:09:34.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 刚刚对你这么凶 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.10,0:09:41.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.30,0:09:44.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经不会再演绎那个虚假的惠了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.88,0:09:49.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我知道了 撒谎只会伤害自己和他人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.45,0:09:53.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不用再看别人脸色行事了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.46,0:09:56.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不用再结识那么多不交心的朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.41,0:10:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要演绎真实的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.87,0:10:01.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.04,0:10:03.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.19,0:10:11.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(283,100)}收藏夹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.19,0:10:09.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(176,139)}【第一】dessert读者板块
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.19,0:10:09.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(204,250)}青年书刊版块
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.61,0:10:09.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要删除1条收藏夹的内容吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.61,0:10:09.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  否
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.54,0:10:10.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已删除
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.68,0:10:11.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(227,142)}东京风尚新闻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.76,0:10:11.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(236,198)}青年书刊版块
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.13,0:10:13.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.72,0:10:16.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠 你把头发剪掉了么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.95,0:10:19.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.37,0:10:22.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想换发型 但没那个勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.70,0:10:26.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是在网上被读者说了就不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.07,0:10:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这有什么不好的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.06,0:10:31.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总在意这些 就没完没了了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.68,0:10:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就永远都做不了自己想做的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.99,0:10:40.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种背后的流言蜚语 用不着这么在意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.85,0:10:44.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要活在现实中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.53,0:11:01.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 打工的时间延长了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.15,0:11:03.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.82,0:11:11.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 季节交替
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.58,0:11:21.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放在哪里了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.33,0:11:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要留下一半哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.38,0:11:41.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快到了呢 夏日祭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.95,0:11:44.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有约会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.56,0:11:45.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.95,0:11:47.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装什么傻呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.72,0:11:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅你去邀请人家也行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.95,0:11:51.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.19,0:11:55.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…你说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.44,0:12:08.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千春 可以下班了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.62,0:12:09.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.91,0:12:10.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅 你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.52,0:12:13.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.19,0:12:14.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是夏日祭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.14,0:12:17.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千春和谁一起去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.43,0:12:18.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.62,0:12:21.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说 千春有男朋友了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.53,0:12:24.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是干嘛不和我说啊 太见外了你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.82,0:12:25.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.22,0:12:28.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏日祭就是今天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.76,0:12:31.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻美给我来消息了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.65,0:12:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 今天去夏日祭吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.46,0:12:38.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去的人…三点在商店街的标志物前？！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.50,0:12:43.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.55,0:12:45.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.32,0:12:47.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.87,0:12:49.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 刚刚在打工
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.81,0:12:51.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 这么突然
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.39,0:12:53.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我想大家一起去 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.73,0:12:54.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.15,0:12:56.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.62,0:12:59.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海和北川呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.13,0:13:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说有事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.52,0:13:03.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪麻美你老这么突然
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.23,0:13:05.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然嘴上这么说 但你不也精心打扮了么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.33,0:13:08.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真像人妻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.72,0:13:10.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱子酱好帅气
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.64,0:13:12.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 大家一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.95,0:13:14.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吃好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.78,0:13:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.12,0:13:21.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苹果糖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.83,0:13:24.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小麻美 吃巧克力香蕉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.73,0:13:25.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.92,0:13:27.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪个都很好吃的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.63,0:13:29.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅 要从哪个开始？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.79,0:13:35.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是也穿浴衣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.70,0:13:46.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅只要和平时一样就足够可爱了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.31,0:13:53.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 在大家面前…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.05,0:13:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.23,0:13:56.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用在意我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.85,0:13:58.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事呀 怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.29,0:14:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么热的天气里你们还这么黏糊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.97,0:14:02.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅 你想吃什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.61,0:14:06.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五平饼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.80,0:14:36.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.11,0:14:38.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我家养了猫了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.27,0:14:40.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是把鱼捞出来就够开心了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.76,0:14:41.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢光顾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.96,0:14:43.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美国热狗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.01,0:14:45.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小麻美 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.03,0:14:47.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙 还能吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.04,0:14:50.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.38,0:14:52.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小麻美 你吃太多了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.89,0:14:54.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是回去休息下好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.12,0:14:56.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.44,0:14:57.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.12,0:15:00.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.50,0:15:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.81,0:15:02.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们接下来怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.24,0:15:04.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等看烟花吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.52,0:15:06.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要等很长时间的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.41,0:15:07.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先回去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.69,0:15:09.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的脚累得快不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.37,0:15:10.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我背你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.77,0:15:12.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也太难看了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.13,0:15:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我们就解散吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.99,0:15:16.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 就这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.50,0:15:17.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息会儿回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.86,0:15:18.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.57,0:15:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别太死撑哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.72,0:15:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.28,0:15:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.65,0:15:31.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅 你去哪里了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.38,0:15:32.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打你手机没有听见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.98,0:15:33.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手机
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.21,0:15:35.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.31,0:15:38.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想帮你穿戴 火急火燎地回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.87,0:15:40.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浴衣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.37,0:15:43.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我估计着你要去夏日祭 所以帮你准备了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.44,0:15:44.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.78,0:15:47.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.99,0:15:51.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才已经去过了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.65,0:15:54.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起啊 还麻烦你特意准备了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.47,0:16:02.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再去一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.08,0:16:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年你不是一个人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.72,0:16:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有大和啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.83,0:16:09.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了 已经和大和…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.22,0:16:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.27,0:16:12.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这身打扮是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.00,0:16:15.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美美地穿上浴衣 再画个妆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.56,0:16:16.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.02,0:16:19.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少在这种日子里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.36,0:16:21.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好地当次女孩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.00,0:16:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的日子里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.39,0:16:25.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了喜欢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.23,0:16:27.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿意付出多少努力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.25,0:16:28.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才是最重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.87,0:16:30.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来帮你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.64,0:16:35.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈只能帮梅做这些
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.36,0:16:39.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 梅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.67,0:16:45.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在 正式开始烟花大会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.56,0:16:48.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在 正式开始烟花大会
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.02,0:17:44.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(神社见)
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.08,0:17:46.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.04,0:18:10.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.74,0:18:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.01,0:18:13.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去不去夏祭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.16,0:18:15.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碰上熟人怪麻烦的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.57,0:18:18.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…已经跟你遇上了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.69,0:18:19.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真过分
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.92,0:18:28.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好美
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.66,0:18:36.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.58,0:18:39.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为什么要跟你一起看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.76,0:18:40.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.21,0:19:07.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好热
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.75,0:19:09.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烟花大会要结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.41,0:19:10.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头发乱糟糟的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.30,0:19:14.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得化了妆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.16,0:19:29.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烟花大会结束了 感谢观赏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.43,0:19:37.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没赶上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.23,0:19:49.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 这时候怎么会想起这些事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.09,0:19:53.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.25,0:19:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人的手很温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.71,0:19:58.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在学校里不顺心的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.36,0:20:03.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总会觉得他们在对我说「会保护你的哦」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.37,0:20:09.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大和
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.26,0:20:18.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.48,0:20:22.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都回去了又突然把你叫出来 真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.66,0:20:24.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.60,0:20:29.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大和
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.92,0:20:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.33,0:20:34.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是觉得你现在超可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.68,0:20:39.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈给我准备了浴衣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.92,0:20:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就穿好过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.60,0:20:43.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然烟花大会结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.31,0:20:46.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我想 无论如何也要让大和看到这样的我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.85,0:20:52.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了 这么无聊的理由叫你出来 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.14,0:20:54.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.31,0:21:17.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不会无聊的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.39,0:21:19.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.68,0:21:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今以后 一定
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.53,0:21:38.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管发生任何事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.64,0:21:46.88,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(976,540)}「会保护你的哦」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.49,0:23:24.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有始就有终 季节更替 时间飞逝
